   - Status
   - Gender
10. Repositories
    - UserRepository
    - OwnerRepository
    - AdminRepository
11. Security / JWT
    - JwtAuthFilter
    - JwtUtil
    - JwtConstants
12. Exceptions
    - GlobalExceptionHandler
    - ApiError
    - AuthException
    - InvalidCredentialsException
    - ResourceAlreadyExistsException
    - UnauthorizedException
13. Utilities
    - PasswordValidator

